        "TileImage": "$($repository e447da3f-0ae7-40fd-ba06-9484159e18a7).Image",
        "Description": "You&apos;re going to need to be quick about this one, 47.\r\rOur client, who has preferred to remain unknown, has asked for you to take out five members of the Mumbai street gang known as the Crows. Specifically, the ones guarding the armory. But you&apos;ll have to be quick. The Crows seem to be aware of this operation, and are sending a group to transfer the weapons to a new, unkown location. Take out the guards, and make sure our client can secure their weaponry.\r\rGodspeed, 47.",
